actions.text: Referred to Senate Committee on Interior and Insular Affairs.

official_title: A bill to amend the act entitled "An Act to authorize the sale of certain public lands in Alaska to the Catholic Bishop of Northern Alaska for use as a mission school," approved August 8, 1953.

summary.text: Deletes the requirement that the public lands transferred by Federal law the Catholic Bishop of Northern Alaska be used as a mission school.
